{
  "texts": [
    "Leader-leader exchanges (LLX) and trust have the largest effect on project and organization performance 96, 97, and explain job satisfaction 98.",
    "Indicators (density, overlap) of the quality of relationships between leaders were included among the characteristics of the candidates.",
    "Based on preliminary qualitative research, we distinguished between SMEs where conflict between managers could be identified due to human relations or professional reasons.",
    "We found that communication relationships between managers were significantly less likely to overlap with the dimension of good leadership evaluation.",
    "The most basic and widely used network structural metrics are degree and centrality."
  ]
}